title: 이달의소녀탐구 #319 (LOONA TV #319)
members: Olivia Hye, Go Won, Chuu, Yves
summary:
Yves, Chuu and Go Won try to guess Olivia’s stage name.
Yves: “Adam?”; Go Won: “Absolutely not!”; Chuu: “A I CHUU WON!” (Yes, she yells as
she proceeds to explain her logic behind it) Go Won copies Chuu and Yves unnie is
done with both of them at this point.
0:13 -- PD tells Hyejoo a few names and she despises them all. The rest keep guess new
names.
